scene.message:
Maki: Wait!{nl}
Where do you think you're{nl}
running? There's nowhere left!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ......{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Those countless bubbles are{nl}
the minds of many people...{waitkey}{clearbox}A human mind is nothing{nl}
but a fragile bubble{nl}
born from this sea...{waitkey}{clearbox}I was a mind that was{nl}
never meant to be born...{waitkey}Had you been born from{nl}
the start, my life would{nl}
have been so different...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Stop it!!{nl}
I don't want to hear{nl}
such words from your mouth!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Did you ever try to change{nl}
yourself? What have you{nl}
even done? Just cried in bed!?{waitkey}{clearbox}I want to change, like you!{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Inaba, Nanjo, Kido...{nl}
and {ctl07:1}...{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't you see, watching them?{nl}
There's nothing you can't do.{waitkey}It's your own heart{nl}
that's ruining everything!{waitkey}{ret}

