Maki: I won't run anymore...{nl}
I'll settle my own{nl}
account myself!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ......{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Take this...{waitkey}It'll let you enter the{nl}
Avidya World, where{nl}
Pandora is.{waitkey}{clearbox}I...{wait_fr:88} of all people,{nl}
I didn't want {ctl07:1}{nl}
to see me like this...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I wonder if I said{nl}
that right...{nl}
But{waitkey}all I can do now is{nl}
believe in myself...{nl}
Let's get back to everyone!{waitkey}{ret}
